column1: #: description: pT-integrated charged kaon to charged pion and proton+antiproton to charged pion production ratios as a function of average multiplicities in p-Pb collisions with centre-of-mass energy/nucleon=5.02 TeV
column2: measured for different V0A multiplicity classes. The first uncertainty is statistical
column3: the second one is the total systematic uncertainty
column4: while the third one is the uncorrelated systematic uncertainty which is multiplicity dependent.
